{
  "stem": "311.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think that more than 200-- 100 or 200 people could-- I don't even think so-- could get in.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, this was in a different quarters, you know, different part of-- it's still in the ghetto city, you know, whatever it is, but it was different kind.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He, Dad spoke to us Yiddish, and we were answering in Polish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yeah, yeah, yeah, my sisters, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- it was regular.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the same as any other place, I think.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But at least it didn't show.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was anti-Semitism, especially when we lived in the quarters on Casimir, yeah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the last two years, they used to come up and-- don't buy by the Jews, and they used to break, you know, the windows.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the Jews were organized, and then you have to hit it back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was time that--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm talking '38, beginning of '39, as the pressure start coming in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "14.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I remember, you know, they-- they broke a few windows, you know, in the stores, but they hardly came out alive, you know?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Came out alive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you know, they start, first time, they'll let them in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They broke it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The second time they came in, they were waiting for them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Had to protect themselves, and they had their ways.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, When I was-- from beginning, I was in a regular school, regular public school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only thing is, you know, there was a rabbi came in once a week for an hour, for us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a Hebrew teacher they would call.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, you know, we were lucky, but you know, when the priest come in and they were teaching them, so we were outside, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
